{"type": "edit", "field": "description", "label": "Description", "before": "\u2022\u00a0STEP TOGETHER provides trauma-informed care, harm reduction, and preventive services such as support groups, individual counseling, and HIV testing to all men of color who have sex with men.\\n\u2022\u00a0HOME AND COMMUNITY-BASED SERVICES (HCBS) helps individuals 21+ with Medicaid to get Psychosocial Rehabilitation, Community Psychiatric Service Treatment, Peer Empowerment, and Habilitation.\\n\u2022\u00a0ASSERTIVE COMMUNITY TEAM (ACT) is for individuals 18+ with Severe and Persistent Mental Health Diagnoses.\\n\u2022\u00a0Youth and family programming for individuals 12-21 years old and their families", "after": "\u2022\u00a0STEP TOGETHER provides trauma-informed care, harm reduction, and preventive services such as support groups, individual counseling, and HIV testing to all men of color who have sex with men.\\n\u2022\u00a0HOME AND COMMUNITY-BASED SERVICES (HCBS) helps individuals 21+ with Medicaid to get Psychosocial Rehabilitation, Community Psychiatric Service Treatment, Peer Empowerment, and Habilitation.\\n\u2022\u00a0ASSERTIVE COMMUNITY TEAM (ACT) is for individuals 18+ with Severe and Persistent Mental Health Diagnoses.\\n\u2022\u00a0Youth and family programming for individuals 12-21 years old and their families", "note": "Updated Description", "summary": "Updated Description", "ts": "2024-08-10T01:30:12Z", "userName": "doobneek", "pagePath": "/team/location/d55706bb-d672-4494-958b-b8cc42632832/services/7e448614-e3ea-4279-95ea-a15f38ebecf7/description", "locationId": "d55706bb-d672-4494-958b-b8cc42632832", "serviceId": "7e448614-e3ea-4279-95ea-a15f38ebecf7", "resourceTable": "services", "action": "update", "copyedit": false}
